"title": "8496: witnessing, importance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8496",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sharing the good news about God and Jesus Christ with others is a work to which some believers have a special calling, but in which all believers are to take part.</p>\n<h2>Witnessing is sharing the truth of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:10-Ps145:12\">PSA 145:10–145:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46-Luke24:48\">LUK 24:46–24:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:7-1Chr16:9\">1CH 16:7–16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:15\">PSA 71:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:54\">MAT 27:54</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:39\">MRK 15:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:47\">LUK 23:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:35-John1:36\">JHN 1:35–1:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:29\">JHN 4:29</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are commanded to witness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:19\">MAT 28:18–28:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:4-Isa12:5\">ISA 12:4–12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:14\">MAT 24:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:10\">MRK 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:15-Acts9:16\">ACT 9:15–9:16</a></p>\n<h2>Special ministries of witnessing</h2>\n<h3>By the prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:6-John1:8\">JHN 1:6–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:4-Jer1:9\">JER 1:4–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:7-Ezek33:9\">EZK 33:7–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:2\">JON 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:9\">JON 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:15\">JHN 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:29\">JHN 1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:36\">JHN 1:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:43\">ACT 10:43</a></p>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:37\">JHN 18:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:31-John3:34\">JHN 3:31–3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>By the apostles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:33\">ACT 4:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:39-Acts10:42\">ACT 10:39–10:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:30-Acts13:31\">ACT 13:30–13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:3\">1JN 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>By Christian leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:8</a></strong> <em>Paul, in prison for his faith, encourages the young leader, Timothy.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:5\">ACT 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11\">EPH 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>Witnessing is a task for all God's people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:6-Ps26:7\">PSA 26:6–26:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:1-Ps107:2\">PSA 107:1–107:2</a>ISA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:10\">43:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:12\">ISA 43:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8\">ISA 44:8</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4\">ACT 8:4</a></p>\n<h2>Witnessing is a major aspect of Christian living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:9–10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:32-Matt10:33\">MAT 10:32–10:33</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">MRK 8:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:8-Luke12:9\">LUK 12:8–12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:13\">2CO 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:23\">1JN 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:15\">1JN 4:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of witnessing to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16\">MAT 16:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:29\">MRK 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:20\">LUK 9:20</a> <em>Simon Peter</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:16-Luke2:17\">LUK 2:16–2:17</a> <em>shepherds</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:40-John1:42\">JHN 1:40–1:42</a> <em>Andrew</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a> <em>Nathanael</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:27\">JHN 11:27</a> <em>Martha</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:28\">JHN 20:28</a> <em>Thomas</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:37\">ACT 8:37</a> <em>the Ethiopian eunuch</em></p>\n<h2>Witnessing recounts personal experience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7\">ISA 63:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:16\">PSA 66:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:10\">JER 51:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:2\">DAN 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:31\">MAT 9:27–9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:40-Mark1:45\">MRK 1:40–1:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:25\">JHN 9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:20\">ACT 4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Witnessing to the resurrection of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:33-Luke24:35\">LUK 24:33–24:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30-Acts5:32\">ACT 5:30–5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:7\">1CO 15:3–15:7</a></p>",
